statements: SELECT * FROM token_transfers;
SELECT token_id, receiver_address, transfer_amount FROM token_transfers WHERE sender_address = '0x123456';
SELECT transfer_id, sender_address, receiver_address FROM token_transfers ORDER BY transfer_timestamp DESC;
SELECT transfer_id, transfer_amount FROM token_transfers WHERE transfer_amount > 1000 ORDER BY transfer_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM token_transfers WHERE sender_address IN ('0x111111', '0x222222') ORDER BY token_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM token_transfers WHERE sender_address = '0x123456789' ORDER BY transfer_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT token_id, sender_address, receiver_address, transfer_amount FROM token_transfers WHERE token_id = 5 ORDER BY transfer_amount DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT transfer_id, sender_address, receiver_address, transfer_timestamp FROM token_transfers WHERE transfer_amount > 10000 ORDER BY transfer_timestamp ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT DISTINCT sender_address, COUNT(*) AS num_transfers FROM token_transfers GROUP BY sender_address HAVING num_transfers > 2 ORDER BY num_transfers DESC;

SELECT transfer_id, sender_address, receiver_address, DATE_FORMAT(transfer_timestamp, '%Y-%m-%d') AS transfer_date FROM token_transfers WHERE transfer_date = '2022-05-15' ORDER BY transfer_id ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM token_transfers;
SELECT transfer_date, sender_address, receiver_address FROM token_transfers;
SELECT token_id, transfer_amount FROM token_transfers WHERE transfer_amount > 100;
SELECT * FROM token_owners ORDER BY owner_id DESC;
SELECT owner_id, token_id, owner_address FROM token_owners WHERE ownership_end_date IS NULL;
SELECT * FROM token_transfers ORDER BY transfer_amount DESC, transfer_date ASC;
SELECT sender_address, receiver_address, transfer_amount FROM token_transfers WHERE token_id='ABC' AND transfer_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30';
SELECT owner_address, ownership_start_date, ownership_end_date FROM token_owners WHERE token_id='XYZ' ORDER BY ownership_end_date DESC;
SELECT token_id, SUM(transfer_amount) AS total_transferred FROM token_transfers GROUP BY token_id HAVING total_transferred > 1000;

SELECT t.token_name, t.total_supply, COUNT(o.ownership_id) AS num_owners FROM tokens t LEFT JOIN token_ownership o ON t.token_id = o.token_id GROUP BY t.token_name, t.total_supply;

SELECT t.token_name, MAX(b.block_timestamp) AS last_block_time FROM tokens t JOIN token_ownership o ON t.token_id = o.token_id JOIN blockchain b ON b.miner_address = o.owner_address GROUP BY t.token_name;
